# Product Packages

## Screens (`src/screens/`)

- Compose `@counseliq/ui` components ‚Äî do not duplicate design-system styles inline.
- Use **v5 semantic color tokens** (`bg-background`, `bg-card`, `text-foreground`, `text-muted-foreground`, `border-border`, `text-primary`) ‚Äî not v3 scales (`bg-background-50`, `text-typography-500`).
- **Button:** `variant="default" | "outline" | "destructive"` ‚Äî not `action="primary"`. **Alert:** `variant="default" | "destructive"`.
- Import auth via `../auth` (`useAuth`). Never import auth from apps.
- Use Solito for navigation: `Link`, `TextLink` from `solito/link`; `useRouter` from `solito/navigation` (Next.js App Router on web).
- Mark screen files with `"use client"` when they use hooks.
- Export new screens from the product package `index.ts`.
- **Safe area:** wrap full-screen roots in `Screen` from `../components/screen`. Use `AuthScreen` for auth forms (login/signup). Never apply `useSafeAreaInsets()` or fixed top padding in screen files ‚Äî `Screen` handles insets.

```tsx
import { Screen } from '../components/screen';

export function MyScreen() {
  return (
    <Screen className="flex-1 bg-background">
      {/* content */}
    </Screen>
  );
}
```

## Auth (`src/auth/`)

- `createAuthProvider` + module-level `useAuth` ‚Äî apps wire token stores via adapters.
- Web adapter: `createLocalStorageTokenStore`. Mobile: `createSecureStoreTokenStore`.
- **User-facing errors:** backend throws `appError(AppErrorCode.X)` from `convex/errors.ts`. UI copy lives in `packages/admin/src/errors/messages.ts` or `packages/client/src/errors/messages.ts`. Use `getUserFacingErrorMessage(error, fallback)` in every `catch` ‚Äî it maps codes only, never reads `error.message`.

```tsx
import { getUserFacingErrorMessage } from '../auth/errors';

try {
  await login(email, password);
} catch (error) {
  setError(getUserFacingErrorMessage(error, 'Login failed. Check your email and password.'));
}
```

## DB (`src/db/`)

- `createConvexClient(url)` for ConvexProvider setup in apps.
- `api` re-exports from `../../../../convex/_generated/api` ‚Äî run `npm run convex:dev` after schema changes.

## Dependencies

- `@counseliq/ui` ‚Äî allowed
- `solito`, `convex` ‚Äî allowed
- Do not add dependencies that belong in apps (Next.js, Expo APIs)
